# Beauty by Raquel Nicole Website Rebuild Project

## Project Context
This is a comprehensive website rebuild for Beauty by Raquel Nicole, a boutique beauty studio specializing in lash extensions and brow treatments. The project involves migrating from a basic Square site to a modern, SEO-optimized platform.

## Key Business Information
- **Business Type:** Boutique beauty studio offering lash extensions, brow treatments, and beauty enhancements
- **Target Audience:** Women aged 18-45 seeking personalized beauty services
- **USP:** Owner-led, high-quality, natural enhancement focus with personalized care
- **Current Issues:** Poor website performance (Lighthouse 11/100), no SEO presence, basic Square template

## Project Goals
- Build modern, fast-loading, mobile-first website (target: Lighthouse 90+)
- Increase local search visibility and Google Maps presence
- Improve brand perception through professional design and testimonials
- Implement marketing automation for repeat bookings

## Technical Stack
- **Frontend:** Next.js with React, TailwindCSS
- **Backend:** Node.js with Express
- **Database:** PostgreSQL with Prisma ORM
- **Hosting:** Vercel (frontend) + AWS/Heroku (backend)
- **Integrations:** Square POS API for bookings/payments

## Brand Identity
- **Colors:** Blush Pink (#F9E6E6), Warm Beige (#F3D7C6), Charcoal Gray (#3C3C3C), Off-White (#FFF8F5), Rose Gold (#C2876C)
- **Typography:** Playfair Display (headers), Lato (body), Montserrat (buttons)
- **Tone:** Confident yet approachable, emphasizing personalized care and natural beauty enhancement

